T02TD1774E:269a-1: shr'i ma h'a k'a la sto tra /
T02TD1774E:269a-3: dpal nag po chen po la bstod pa /
T02TD1774E:269a-4: dpal nag po chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1774E:269a-5: h'um srin po'i gzugs kyis gdug pa can //
T02TD1774E:269b-0: tshar gcod byang chub @269b sems dpa' ste //
T02TD1774E:269b-1: grong khyer sum brtsegs 'jig byed pa'i //
T02TD1774E:269b-2: gtum po khyod la bdag bstod do //
T02TD1774E:269b-3: mdog nag gzugs thung gzi brjid can //
T02TD1774E:269b-4: gdug pa tshar gcod gri gug g-yas //
T02TD1774E:269b-5: g-yon pa gdug pa'i khrag bkang snod //
T02TD1774E:269b-6: thod phreng can la bdag bstod do //
T02TD1774E:269b-7: khros pas zhabs brdabs sa gzhi g-yo //
T02TD1774E:269b-8: 'jigs pa'i gad mos ri rab bsgyel //
T02TD1774E:269b-9: dam tshig nyams pa'i snying 'byin pa //
T02TD1774E:269b-10: dam tshig can la bdag bstod do //
T02TD1774E:269b-11: h'um zhal gcig pa la phyag gnyis pa //
T02TD1774E:269b-12: gri gug thod pa lag na 'dzin //
T02TD1774E:269b-13: ral pa kham nag gyen du 'khyil //
T02TD1774E:269b-14: spyan gsum me yi mdog 'dra ba //
T02TD1774E:269b-15: mche ba zla ba tshes pa 'dra //
T02TD1774E:269b-16: thod pa'i phreng bas do shal byas //
T02TD1774E:269b-17: gsus khyim che la 'phyang ba po //
T02TD1774E:269b-18: mi thung khros pa'i gzugs 'dra ba //
T02TD1774E:269b-19: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
T02TD1774E:269b-20: bstan ba srung bar zhal bzhes pa //

T02TD1774E:269b-22: gdug pa tshar gcod 'jigs pa'i gzugs //

T02TD1774E:269b-24: steng gi lha tshogs 'jigs par byed //
T02TD1774E:269b-25: spyan bgrad mche gtsigs ljags 'dril bas //
T02TD1774E:269b-26: bar gyi gdon tshogs bsdigs par byed //
T02TD1774E:269b-27: g-yas na gri gug bsnams pa ni //
T02TD1774E:269b-28: dgra bgegs 'dul zhing bdud mgo gcod //
T02TD1774E:269b-29: g-yon pas thod pa bsnams pa ni //
T02TD1774E:269b-30: gnod sems can gyi khrag bkang gsol //
T02TD1774E:269b-31: khros pa'i zhabs gnyis brdab pa yis //
T02TD1774E:269b-32: gnod sems can gyi lus la nyed //
T02TD1774E:269b-33: khyod kyis thub pa'i bstan pa srungs //
T02TD1774E:269b-34: rnal 'byor pa yi bar chad srungs //
T02TD1774E:269b-35: chos dang dpal 'byor rgyas par mdzod //
T02TD1774E:269b-36: lus dang grib ma bzhin du 'grogs //
T02TD1774E:269b-37: dpal nag po chen po la bstod pa slob dpon bram ze mchog sred kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so//
